Class ResultUseRule<C,S>

java.lang.Object
com.google.errorprone.bugpatterns.checkreturnvalue.ResultUseRule<C,S>
Type Parameters:
C - the type of the context object used during evaluation
S - the type of symbols
Direct Known Subclasses:
ResultUseRule.GlobalRule, ResultUseRule.MethodRule, ResultUseRule.SymbolRule
public abstract class ResultUseRule<C,S> extends Object
A rule for determining ResultUsePolicy for methods and/or constructors.
